OL,8,Ftwo sleeping students and a teacher
OL,9,Fwith hammers told one of his alleged
OL,10,Fvictims he was storing weapons for the
OL,11,F"apocalypse", a court heard.
OL,13,FThe 16-year-old was wearing just his
OL,14,Fboxer shorts when he is said to have
OL,16,FExeter Crown Court heard how the
OL,17,Fteenager, who cannot be identified for
OL,18,Flegal reasons, armed himself with
OL,19,Fthree claw hammers.
