OL,7,F"(Name) asked me had I asked the
OL,8,Fdefendant why he had got a hammer in
OL,9,Fhis room, and he had said he had got
OL,10,Fthe idea of the apocalypse, and he was
OL,11,Fpreparing for the apocalypse," the boy
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"The other time was the Christmas term
OL,15,Flast year and things had gone missing
OL,16,Fand there were searches and Mr Roffe-
OL,17,FSilvester found his hammers and (name)
OL,18,Fsaid to me the excuse the defendant
OL,19,Fgave was the apocalypse.
