OL,7,F"He kept mentioning in computer
OL,8,Fscience about the apocalypse and how
OL,9,Fit was going to happen in 2023 or
OL,10,F2024."
OL,12,FThe boy was asked about a knife that
OL,13,Fhad been recovered from his bed after
OL,14,Fthe attack and he said he knew nothing
OL,15,Fabout it.
OL,17,FThe defendant, now aged 17, denies
OL,18,Fthree charges of attempted murder.
OL,20,FThe trial continues.
